Our BIGGEST update to Penman is available now! We have recreated Penman from ground up bringing a new experience while maintaining Penman s core values. let s dive into the new features: Continuity Now you can have Penman on all of your devices: iPhone iPad and Mac taking you to a whole new level of efficiency. Universe Purchase Purchase premium once and enjoy it on all your devices no matter iPhone iPad or even Mac Fresh Design With this version we ve modernized and revamped almost every part of Penman. Giving users a whole new experience while maintaining our commitment to a simplicity and efficiency. New Sync system We ve developed a whole new save and sync system for premium users to make sure you never loose your notes. Trash Your notes will now be added to the trash after you delete them. You can recover deleted notes from the trash. New Editor We have completely revamped our editor system. New Notebooks Make sure to checkout our new Notebooks more beautiful than ever and still the best place to save your notes. Be sure to download the update and enjoy Penman!

We wanted to take an opportunity to thank our community for reaching out and their patience bringing these issues to our attention. This update FIXES all the crashes.
